dual test.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The reported javaTest failure is a behavioral assertion change in ObjectPropertyAccessor for 3.3.5, not evidence of a missing dependency or external service.\",\n    \"SecurityManager-based coverage is JDK-version-sensitive because SecurityManager APIs are deprecated for removal.\",\n    \"Expression compiler coverage uses Javassist and may need native-image-specific handling even though it is available on the JVM classpath transitively.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a2290e9206759e9016a40ecf7d54881938da6179a28bd485f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1550, "output": 1326, "cacheRead": 45568, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 48444, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782639851197, "responseId": "resp_0a2290e9206759e9016a40ecebad0c81938df35d9fd051f4d8"}, "toolResults": []}
